Jet) 等航空公司都面临延误。包括塔塔星巴克在内的零售商都遇到了 PoS 问题。金融市场受到扰乱。 CrowdStrike 首席执行官乔治·库尔茨 (George Kurtz) 道歉。西亚兰·马丁强调脆弱性。普华永道称其为“黑天鹅事件”。 PhonePe 的 Share.market 面临问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 21:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/crowdstrike-shuts-down-worlds-windows-for-hours/articleshow/111871436.cms</guid></item><item><title>移民船在海地海岸起火 造成40人死亡、数人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/40-dead-several-injured-after-migrant-boat-catches-fire-off-haiti-coast/articleshow/111875107.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111875107.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;海地北部海岸发生悲惨事件，40 名移民的船着火，夺去了他们的生命。海地不断升级的暴力和贫困导致移民增加，仅今年就有超过 86,000 名移民被迫返回。国际努力旨在稳定危机中的国家。国际移民组织驻海地代表团团长格雷瓜尔·古德斯坦表示：“海地的社会经济状况十分痛苦。” “过去几个月的极端暴力只会让海地人更加采取绝望的措施。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 01:42:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/40-dead-several-injured-after-migrant-boat-catches-fire-off-haiti-coast/articleshow/111875107.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登的家人正在讨论2024年底的竞选，27名议员敦促他退出：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bidens-family-discussing-end-to-2024-run-as-27-lawmakers-urge-him-to-drop-out-report/articleshow/111871375.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111871375.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 21:26:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bidens-family-discussing-end-to-2024-run-as-27-lawmakers-urge-him-to-drop-out-report/articleshow/111871375.cms</guid></item><item><title>五月太阳超级风暴引发历史上最大规模的卫星“大规模迁移”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/may-solar-superstorm-triggered-largest-satellite-mass-migration-in-history/articleshow/111871249.cms</link><description>&