first-female-stratosphere-skydive-pushed-to-2026/articleshow/111869330.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么特朗普枪击受害者科里·康佩托雷的名字在共和党全国委员会消防员制服上被拼错</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/why-trump-shooting-victim-corey-comperatores-name-was-misspelled-on-firefighter-uniform-at-rnc/articleshow/111868955.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111868955.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:24:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/why-trump-shooting-victim-corey-comperatores-name-was-misspelled-on-firefighter-uniform-at-rnc/articleshow/111868955.cms</guid></item><item><title>尽管面临巨大压力，拜登“绝对”留在美国总统竞选中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/president-joe-biden-to-campaign-again-amid-democratic-nomination-talks/articleshow/111868103.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111868103.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 15:19:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/president-joe-biden-to-campaign-again-amid-democratic-nomination-talks/articleshow/111868103.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着抗议活动变得暴力，BSF 从孟加拉国营救印度学生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/bsf-rescues-indian-students-from-bangladesh-as-protests-turn-violent/articleshow/111867922.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111867922.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 15:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/bsf-rescues-indian-students-from-bangladesh-as-protests-turn-violent/articleshow/111867922.cms</guid></item><item><title>从纽约到伦敦、巴黎的医院都在技术中断中苦苦挣扎</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hospitals-from-new-york-to-london-paris-struggle-in-tech-outage/articleshow/111867131.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111867131.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于全球数字中断导致程序取消和对手写记录的依赖，世界各地的卫生系统面临中断。美国和英国的主要医院在获取重要医疗数据时遇到困难。新罕布什尔州的紧急服务暂时受到影响。网络事件归因于软件更新问题，对各行业造成广泛影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 14:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hospitals-from-new-york-to-london-paris-struggle-in-tech-outage/articleshow/111867131.cms</guid></item><item><title>越南任期最长的越共中央总书记阮富仲去世，享年80岁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nguyen-phu-trong-vietnams-longest-serving-party-chief-passes-away-at-80/articleshow/111864345.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111864345.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;担任越南共产党总书记13年的阮​​富仲去世，享年80岁。苏林主席接任职务。受过苏联教育的阮富仲自 2011 年起担任总统，并于 2021 年第三次连任。他发起了 2017 年的反腐败运动，但最近显得脆弱。政党必须在 2026 年国会之前决定林郑月娥的角色，或者选择新的候选人。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 12:13:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nguyen-phu-trong-vietnams-longest-serving-party-chief-passes-away-at-80/articleshow/111864345.cms</guid></item><item><title>孟加拉国因公务员招聘规则引发暴力抗议：主要事态发展</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/violent-protest-grips-bangladesh-over-civil-service-hiring-rules-top-developments/articleshow/111860420.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111860420.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;孟加拉国周五宣布实施宵禁，并部署军队，此前警方未能平息全国蔓延的多日致命骚乱。哈西娜的新闻秘书纳伊穆尔·伊斯兰·汗告诉法新社：“政府已决定实行宵禁并部署军队来援助民政当局。”他补充说，宵禁将立即生效。首都达卡警方早些时候采取了严厉措施，禁止当天所有公共集会——这是抗议活动开始以来的第一次——以防止更多暴力事件发生。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:10:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/violent-protest-grips-bangladesh-over-civil-service-hiring-rules-top-developments/articleshow/111860420.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国利兹发生骚乱，公交车被纵火：是什么导致了骚乱？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/riot-breaks-out-in-uks-leeds-bus-set-ablaze-what-led-to-the-unrest/articleshow/111856781.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111856781.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;利兹发生大规模骚乱，抗议者推翻警车并纵火焚烧双层巴士。西约克郡警方对哈尔希尔斯卢克索街正在发生的事件做出回应。随着局势升级，官员将机构工作人员和儿童转移到安全的地方。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:08:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/riot-breaks-out-in-uks-leeds-bus-set-ablaze-what-led-to-the-unrest/articleshow/111856781.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普家族的统一战线在共和党全国委员会大放异彩，梅拉尼娅、伊万卡及孙辈登台</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-familys-united-front-shines-at-rnc-with-melania-ivanka-grandchildren-on-stage/articleshow/111853699.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111853699.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特朗普家族在共和党全国委员会上展现了统一战线，梅拉尼娅和伊万卡与这位前总统一起上台。梅拉尼娅罕见的公开露面和伊万卡缺席竞选公告引发了人们对她们政治未来的质疑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:58:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-familys-united-front-shines-at-rnc-with-melania-ivanka-grandchildren-on-stage/articleshow/111853699.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>